    <published>2016-01-01T14:58:12.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-01-07T14:51:39.262Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>系统环境<br>Windows 10 专业版</p>
<h1 id="u4E0B_u8F7D_u5B89_u88C5"><a href="#u4E0B_u8F7D_u5B89_u88C5" class="headerlink" title="下载安装"></a>下载安装</h1><p><a href="https://git-for-windows.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://git-for-windows.github.io/</a></p>
<h1 id="u73AF_u5883_u53D8_u91CF"><a href="#u73AF_u5883_u53D8_u91CF" class="headerlink" title="环境变量"></a>环境变量</h1><pre><code class="bash">C:\Program Files\Git\cmd;
C:\Program Files\Git\mingw64\bin;C:\Program Files\Git\usr\bin;
</code></pre>
<h1 id="u914D_u7F6E"><a href="#u914D_u7F6E" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h1><p><strong>申请Github账号</strong><br><a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/</a></p>
<p><strong>设置Git的username和email</strong></p>
<pre><code class="bash">$ git config --global user.name <span class="string">"username"</span>
$ git config --global user.email <span class="string">"name@org.com"</span>
$ git config --list
</code></pre>
<p><strong>生成密钥</strong></p>
<pre><code class="bash">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"name@org.com"</span>
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Github添加ssh key</strong><br>Account Settings -&gt; SSH Keys -&gt; Add SSH key</p>
<p><strong>验证ssh key</strong></p>
<pre><code class="bash">$ ssh -T git@github.com
</code></pre>
]]></content>
